AA-12 (Automatic Assault Shotgun)

Link to wiki page on the AA-12: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atchisson_Assault_Shotgun

Weapon code needed:BL2(BwAAAAAv/AAWEWqgwxBQ6AHEBEQHBFfE//////////9WxA3EWsQ=)


High accuracy (for a shotgun)
Accuracy decreases slowly with continues fire
32 Round drum mag
5.0 Firerate
High damage
Low recoil
Black Skin
########################################################
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.A_Weapons_Legendary.SG_Bandit_5_SledgesShotgun:WeaponPartListCollectionDefinition_135 BarrelPartData (bEnabled=True,WeightedParts=((Part=WeaponPartDefinition'GD_Weap_Shotgun.Barrel.SG_Barrel_Hyperion_Striker',Manufacturers=,MinGameStageIndex=0,MaxGameStageIndex=1,DefaultWeightIndex=2)))

